                        </div>
                        <hr class="mb-8">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-5">
                            <h4 class="max-w-[160px] text-[1.25rem] font-bold">Odhadovaná mesačná suma</h4>
                            <h2 class="text-[2rem] font-bold" id="mes_sum">389€</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-[1.25rem]">Vybavte si rýchlu <span class="text-dRed">pôžičku</span> už
                                dnes a <span class="text-dRed">bez poplatkov</span></p>
                        </div>
                        <hr class="mt-8">
                        <div class="flex mt-[1rem] text-white">
